    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-80e7-9d2e-dbd4532a494b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Learning for individuals depends on many factors but assessments often are one-size fits all approaches. Thus, recommending assessments in a personalized way would be very helpful. The work proposes an autonomous agent-based approach for recommendations of assessment tasks:",
